{"type":"article","id":4288,"title":"品葱上的“新无神论六骑士”","uid":6760,"topics":[8,210],"contents":"两组三胞胎们：<br>\n<br>\n出生入死：<br>\n<a href=\"https://pincong.rocks/people/矢作萌夏\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">矢作萌夏</a><br>\n<a href=\"https://pincong.rocks/people/纸月之王\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">纸月之王</a><br>\n<a href=\"https://pincong.rocks/people/天龍男\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">天龍男</a><br>\n<br>\n后起之秀：<br>\n<a href=\"https://pincong.rocks/people/可爱猴猴\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">可爱猴猴</a><br>\n<a href=\"https://pincong.rocks/people/巧克力袿姬\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">巧克力袿姬</a><br>\n<a href=\"https://pincong.rocks/people/博多堺\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">博多堺</a><br>\n<br>\n前一组是字面意义上的出生入死，他们都有被观察（过），纸月之王海被怀疑过是矢作萌夏的小号。他们是前两个月的反宗教主力，因为当时法轮功兴盛，所以主要反法轮功。<br>\n后来品葱法轮功十支柱之二“<a href=\"https://pincong.rocks/people/永不放弃\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">永不放弃</a>”和“<a href=\"https://pincong.rocks/people/千年暗室一灯明\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">千年暗室一灯明</a>”分别因魔怔、骂人和性骚扰鹿儿被黑名单，法轮功势微，基督教崛起。<br>\n于是后一组，也就是这个月的反宗教主力，因为基督教兴盛，所以主要反基督教。这三位后起之秀也都没被观察过。","date":"2020-11-26","agreeCount":1,"discussionCount":0}